Todayâ€™s websites are dynamic, ever-changing environments centered around objectives and goals. But how do you know if you are meeting those goals or what should be changed on your website? Google Analytics can open businesses up to an incredible amount of information about site viewers and consumer behavior including most and least visited pages, where your visitors are located, how they are finding your website, your bounce rate and your best referrers.

Presented by Derek Allard, Gravity Switch, Northampton
